race.description: Now Racing Every Wednesday At Dundalk Handicap (0-60)
race.comment: MASKED ANGEL (1) did well last time finishing third tackling 1005m at this track after being slow out when leaving the stalls. Longer trip may play to her strengths and she looks the one to beat. HAPPY HENRY (11) lifted strongly only just failing to pass the winner last start over 1207m at Navan. Going well and holds genuine winning claims. JAZZY DANCER (5) improved in latest finishing 2.75L behind in third attempting 1408m here after travelling well on the bend. Key player. HERO OF THE HOUR (4) was beaten 3.5L fourth in a 1207m contest here. Best efforts measure up so is worth giving another chance.
